function.name: Receive SignOn
function.responseScript: ext.FMTI = '1814' ext.F7 = saved.F7 ext.F11 = saved.F11 ext.F12 = saved.F12 ext.F24 = '801' ext.F39 = '800' channel.self_signon = 'true' channel.peer_signon = 'true' return 1

function.name: Send SignOn
function.requestScript: ext.FMTI = '1804' ext.F7 = formatDate('MMddHHmmss') ext.F11 = endpointSequence('stan') ext.F12 = formatDate('YYMMddHHmmss') ext.F24 = '801' channel.self_signon = 'true' channel.peer_signon = 'true' endpoint."${ctx.channel_id}".logged_on = 'true' return 1

function.name: Receive Echo
function.responseScript: ext.FMTI = '1814' ext.F7 = saved.F7 ext.F11 = saved.F11 ext.F12 = saved.F12 ext.F24 = '831' ext.F39 = '800' channel.self_signon = 'true' return 1

function.name: Send Echo
function.requestScript: ext.FMTI = '1804' ext.F7 = formatDate('MMddHHmmss') ext.F11 = endpointSequence('stan') ext.F12 = formatDate('YYMMddHHmmss') ext.F24 = '831' return 1

function.name: Receive Sign Off
function.responseScript:
ext.FMTI = '1814' ext.F7 ?= saved.F7 ext.F11 ?= saved.F11 ext.F12 ?= saved.F12 ext.F24 ?= saved.F24 ext.F39 = '800' channel.self_signon = 'true'
return true

function.name: Send Sign Off
function.requestScript: ext.FMTI = '1804' ext.F7 = formatDate('MMddHHmmss') ext.F11 = endpointSequence('stan') ext.F12 = formatDate('YYMMddHHmmss') ext.F24 = '802' endpoint."${ctx.channel_id}".logged_on = 'false' channel.self_signon = 'false' channel.peer_signon ='false' return 1

function.name: User SignOn
function.requestScript: ext.FMTI = '1804' ext.F7 = formatDate('MMddHHmmss') ext.F11 = endpointSequence('stan') ext.F12 = formatDate('YYMMddHHmmss') ext.F24 = '801' endpoint."${ctx.channel_id}".logged_on = 'true' channel.self_signon = 'true' channel.peer_signon ='true' return 1
